        "author_name": "Management Information System Mahavir",
        "rating": 5,
        "review": "I have been associated with Shree Mahavir Fabrics MFG Co., and I must say they truly deliver excellence in shirting fabrics. Established in 1999, their years of experience clearly reflect in the quality, finishing, and consistency of their products.\nThey offer a wide range of plain, printed, and dobby shirting fabrics, all of which are durable, colorfast, and skin-friendly. The team is professional, supportive, and always keeps up with the latest market trends.\nTheir commitment to quality and timely delivery makes them one of the most reliable fabric manufacturers in the industry.\nHighly recommended for anyone looking for premium shirting fabrics.",
        "time_ago": "3 weeks ago"
      },
      {
        "author_name": "Hetal Rathod",
        "rating": 5,
        "review": "I recently purchased some fabric from Shree Mahavir Fabrics and I was impressed with the quality. The variety they offer is quite good, especially for traditional wear. Definitely a place to check out in Ahmedabad.",
        "time_ago": "4 weeks ago"
      }
